body.section:
Backup KVM-region system files If the KVM region controller username/password is set other than defaults, use the Attis CLI to update those values in the KVM region controller config.
attis config --id <config_id of WR_Appliance_system_files_Backup> --update-parameter '{"wr_controller_backup_user":"YOUR_USER"}' attis config --id <config_id of WR_Appliance_system_files_Restore> --update-parameter '{"wr_controller_backup_password":"YOUR_PASSWORD"}
Thenattis backup --config-id <Config_ID_of_ WR_Appliance_system_files_Backup>
